captions.text:
Be a chap and take this
poem to my fat wife.

Would you take THIS poem
to MY wife?

Actually, I haven't finished it yet.
What rhymes with 'divorce'?

Can you help me find the pin
to this grenade?

Is there anyone here who
DOESN'T have a fatal injury?!

-Read my fortune!
-You never take me anywhere nice...

I served with your husband in
the Space Marines and...
he wanted me to read you this poem.

"I want a divorce...
because you look like a horse."

There's...fatal wou--oh, he's already dead.
I'm just talking to myself.
